data.description: Welcome to Eagle Trace in the  Lakewood Ranch area. No cdd fees !Low HOA fees including gated community, amenities, and maintenance free. This villa was built in 2014 and features 2 bedrooms plus den and 2 car garage. Spacious open floor plan! This villa is move in ready . Extended lanai overlooks a deep lot and peek of a lake. Beautiful silver palms behind the home. Upon entry you will notice the beautiful French doors opening into the den with a lot of natural light. Across the way is a guest bedroom with brand new carpet with a walk in closet. A charming guest bath adjacent to the laundry room and guest bedroom. Walk through to the large kitchen open to the dining room with lots of space , and great room ideal for entertaining with sliders . Beautiful tray ceiling with bamboo encompasses the ceiling. Proceed to the primary suite with plank floor crown molding throughout, plantation shutters,California closets added to his and her closets. Dual sinks Greet you as this bathroom is handicapped accessible. Bars in bathroom and walk in shower.  You will also find ceiling fans in every room. So many upgrades in the garage including whole house water softener and built in closets along with epoxy floor and mud sink. Please make sure to check out the amenities with resort style pool , spa, tennis court/ Pickleball and 2 dog parks . The home is conveniently located near shopping, entertainment,restaurants, medical facilities , schools and interstate 10 minutes away.
data.whatILove: A beautiful bright light colors throughout split floor plan attatched villa. 2 bedrooms plus office flex room with beautiful French doors. All rooms are tile . One bedroom has brand new carpet. Garage has built in shelves , epoxy floors. Plenty of upgrades throughout the villa. Upgrades include water softener system, plantation shutters throughout the villa, crown molding , tray ceiling , California closets in master bedroom. Ceiling fans in every room . Wired to hang tv on walls. Pavers in extended lanai. A beautiful gated community with no CDD, low taxes and low HOA. Situated on a cul- de -sac . All it needs is a new family .
